    public static class SpansList.Span
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<SpansList.Span>
    A Span represents an interval of time with millisecond precision. Spans are used by HoldingsList and GapsList to represent both holdings and the gaps between them.
    See Also:
    HoldingsList, GapsList
